# Demo 01: Running the vote-service with docker

- Move to the vote-service directory

```
cd ./services/vote
```

- Build the vote-service image

```
docker build -t leonjalfon1/k8s-demo-vote:latest .
```

- Run the image localy

```
docker run -p 5000:80 leonjalfon1/k8s-demo-vote:latest
```

- Browse to the vote portal

```
http://localhost:5000
```